{"tid":1019623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長假後唔想返學　15歲仔灣仔寓所危站","createTime":"2019-02-13T05:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T06:13:06.000Z","uid":196627,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"41d58209be3623a1d1ced2da6370bd7f70fd8ce7","tid":1019623,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:18:10.000Z","msg":"灣仔有少年危站窗外。今早(13日)7時22分，聖佛蘭士街33號萬豪閣一中層單位，一名15歲少年，突然情緒激動，爬出窗外危站，其姓陳(53歲)母親見狀大驚報警。警員及消防員到場，經20分鐘游說，將事主勸服救返屋內。他沒有受傷，但為安全起見，由救護車送院檢查，警方正調查少年危站原因。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，事主為美、台混血兒，在國際學校讀書，今早在新春長假後，因有功課未完，不想返學與家人爭執，期間情緒激動走到窗邊危站，家人見狀報警。 <br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線： <br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222 <br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000 <br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288 <br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255 <br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000 <br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281 <br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350 <br />\n利民會： 3512 2626 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190213/bkn-20190213075345887-0213_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190213%2Fbkn-20190213075345887-0213_00822_001.html&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwiRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=c6c04a5c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190213/bkn-20190213075345887-0213_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c3369eba8d5fe5e01163cbe7e345ef2f7afaaf69","tid":1019623,"uid":196627,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:18:17.000Z","msg":"我夠唔想翻工喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b4dfc7f8ea953f2492701a90d57bf30b38e354","tid":1019623,"uid":53122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:20:47.000Z","msg":"早d死"},{"pid":"8ce7914725ac07ee5351db0354af583cecc07ba8","tid":1019623,"uid":200280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"我想同佢調轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5869025879667e98a8f1360f7d367c7d085386a","tid":1019623,"uid":228143,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score